        <p>All of Leeds — Headingley, Roundhay, Horsforth, Chapel Allerton, Morley, Pudsey — plus Bradford, Wakefield, Huddersfield, Harrogate, and York. Full list on our <a href="/areas/">areas page</a>.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="faq-item">
        <h3>How do I get started?</h3>
        <p>Grab the <a href="/free-seo-audit-leeds/">free audit</a>. We analyse your site, competitors, and local landscape, then deliver a prioritised action plan. No commitment. <a href="/contact/">Get in touch</a> to kick things off.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="cta-box">
        <h2>Get the Audit</h2>
        <p>Find out where your Leeds business stands in search. We analyse your site, benchmark your competitors, and deliver a clear action plan. No jargon. No obligation.</p>
        <p><a href="/free-seo-audit-leeds/">Get the Free Audit</a></p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Base>
